HEADWORD: cronstedtite
<hw>cron"stedt*ite</hw> <pr>(kr⟦ocr⟧n"st⟦ecr⟧t*⟦imac⟧t)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A mineral consisting principally of
